data.description:
Live large in this delightful & spacious residence with marvelous panoramic mountain views & gorgeous sunsets. VSF is ideally located between Sedona & Cottonwood with easy access to I-17. The community sports a golf course & two large clubhouses with pools, gyms, game rooms, & BBQ's. This wonderful home lives much larger than the square footage might suggest, with 3 bedrooms plus a capacious study. The primary suite features grand views & a huge walk-in closet. Your family's  chef will love the generous & well-crafted kitchen design, featuring an island & a formal, yet open, dining room with a bay window. Fabulous outdoor living with great landscaping & an extra large & well-appointed back patio with one of the best views at VSF. Some furnishings available, including both dining sets. What we love about our home:
We are enthralled by the wonderful and expansive views and the awesome evening sunsets.
We just love our front yard with the largest Saguaro cactus in the neighborhood.
We appreciate the extra bedroom enabling us to have an office and a study.
We like the feeling and the spaciousness that the open floor concept gives us.
We appreciate the new extended patio and being able to dine outdoors.
We love our wonderful neighbors.
Anthony and Lydia Johnson

Other Lifestyle Bonuses:
*Marvelous Indoor-Outdoor Living with large extended back patio with one of the Very Best Views in Verde Santa Fe.
*Delightful, yet low maintenance landscaping, Saguaros and Views.
*Heavy Duty, impenetrable, front Security Screen Door allows you to leave your front door open at night to catch the cool summer breezes with no worries.
*Light and airy feel to the home with great views from Living Room, Primary Suite, Guest Bedroom, even the Kitchen and Dining Room. Excellent Feng Shui.
